INSERT INTO DEPENDENTS_PHONE (
    ID,
    SUBS_ID,
    HOF_ID,
    PHONE_NUMBER,
    CREATED_DATE,
    FLG_ENABLE
) VALUES (
    DEPENDENTS_PHONE_SEQ.NEXTVAL,
    {{ subsTable.selectedRow.ID }},         -- subscriber id
    {{ dep_table.selectedRow.ID }},         -- hof id
    '{{ PhoneInput1.dialCode }}{{ PhoneInput1.text }}',  -- concatenated phone
    SYSDATE,
    1
)
